              <li><strong>STR Zoning Questions:</strong> Susie Spry, Manager of Enforcement Services, 905-873-2600 ext. 2213, <a href="mailto:susies@haltonhills.ca">susies@haltonhills.ca</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

